cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the exploration of game state spaces, which is a problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and game theory (cs.GT). The authors also propose a metric for quantifying exploration quality, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the semantic map of reachable states in a game, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and software development (cs.SD).
